description:
Is the Mark of the Beast a Computer Chip? - If you Google, “What is the Mark of the Beast?”, you will discover lots of interpretations online. Perhaps the most popular view is that the mark of the beast is a microchip, or similar high-tech device. Pastor Wohlberg reveals what the Holy Bible actually teaches, contrary to modern myths.

Recorded live at the 3ABN Spring Camp Meeting 2017: "Exposing the Counterfeit."
